txt.en: Shadow runes and torches can be found within Kidzul-kâlah's depths.\n\nYou should destroy the shadow runes and torches that you find.
Shadow runes and torches can be found within Kidzul-kâlah's depths.\n\nYou should destroy the shadow runes and torches that you find.

Shadows haunt the ruins of Kidzul-kâlah. The darkness has set in to even the old statues and obelisks that decorate the aqueducts of the dwarf-made water-house. The shadow must be purged from these old ruins if exploration is to continue.
You have destroyed the mysterious shadow runes that plague Kidzul-kâlah's depths. In return you have made the interior of Kidzul-kâlah safer to explore. Varthmath will be pleased with your efforts.
